query:
SELECT d.id as valid_doc_id, d.name, p.documentId as project_doc_id, COUNT(*) as project_count 
FROM documents d 
LEFT JOIN projects p ON p.documentId != d.id OR p.documentId IS NULL
GROUP BY d.id, d.name, p.documentId;
